Content:




Published Saturday, 2025-12-13, including PRs merged Friday, 2025-12-05 through Thursday, 2025-12-11.
’Щ@b805a43b4058fc6291798ce1628af5e9ebf277bb1e03502c5b657f7b0cff4209Ъ	Title: title: 'This week in Nushell #329'
Path: Nushell
Content:
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17149] updated explore regex command to look more helpful and professional (#17149)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17133] bumped the rust-toolchain to 1.90.0 (#17133)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17139] bumped bytesize from 2.1.0 to 2.3.1 (#17139)
@andrewgazelka:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17132] added $history variable and structured response format (#17132)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17121] added REPL-style state persistence across evaluations (#17121)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17120] refactored mcp to extract tool descriptions to markdown files (#17120)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17119] switched mcp to output NUON format instead of expanded string (#17119)
@hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17131] upgraded nushell to 0.109.1 for release and nightly workflow (#17131)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17126] fixed 
``table -i false``
 panic when there is an index column (#17126)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17125] fixed http DNS resolution 'Service not supported' error in Docker containers (#17125)
@WindSoilder:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17130] prevented merge_predecl from moving all predecls to overlay (#17130)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17103] made --env-config and --config errors lead to error status code when running nu scripts (#17103)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17052] fixed pipefail behavior inside try block (#17052)
@NotTheDr01ds:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17129] changed home-path/temp-path to home-dir/temp-dir (#17129)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17127] added record conversion to 
``into list``
 (#17127)
@ayax79:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17116] added Azure blob storage support for polars (#17116)
@KaiSforza:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17084] updated flake.lock and added 
``latest``
 devshell variant (#17084)
@sgvictorino:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17058] used 
``Stack::get_config()``
 in more places (#17058)
